Faith Obazuaye (amụrụ na  uboch nke anọ  n' onwa Machị 1989) bụ onye Naijiria na-egwu egwu Tenis tebụl
O sonyere Naịjirịa na asọmpi tenis tebul nke obodo na nke mba ụwa
Obazuaye sonyere na asọmpi emere na afọ 2018 Egwuregwu Commonwealebee o anọchitere  anya Naijiria.

Obazuaye bụ onye Naijiria na-egwuregwu  tenis table 10, ọ sonyere na otu Ụmụ nwanyị 10 na asọmpi   tabulu tenis nke ụmụ nwanyị nke ndi commonwealth haziri na 2018 N'ime Gold Coast, Australia ebe ọ meriri ma nwetakwa ọlaọcha. Obazuaye bụ naanị nwanyị Naijiria ruru eru maka 2020 Summer Paralympics mgbe ọ rụchara ọrụ na asọmpi nke mba Africa nke eji 2019 ITTF African Championship wee mara.
A mụrụ Faith dị ka Faith Oba-zuaye na 4 Machị 1989 na Benin City isi obodo Edo State, Nijiria.
